          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1863.-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the <strong>basa</strong> from the <span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>baking paper</strong></span> and serve over the <strong>cauliflower mash</strong> with the <strong>sweet potatoes</strong> on the side</p>\n<p>Spoon over the <strong>spring onions</strong>, <strong>capers</strong> and any <strong>remaining juices</strong> from the parcel</p>\n<p>Enjoy!<br /> </p>",
